      <title>美联储报告称小企业在 2023 年面临财务和通胀挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/fed-report-says-small-businesses-faced-financial-inflation-challenges-2023-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12家地区联邦储备银行周四发布的一份报告显示，去年小企业继续从疫情大流行的打击中恢复过来，同时面临着利率上升带来的财务挑战以及仍然难以找到工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/fed-report-says-small-businesses-faced-financial-inflation-challenges-2023-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
