      <title>欧盟行业负责人表示，苹果与 Epic Games 的争端是当务之急</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-epic-games-spat-is-matter-priority-eu-industry-chief-says-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟行业负责人蒂埃里·布雷顿 (Thierry Breton) 周四表示，欧盟监管机构的任务是优先调查苹果与《堡垒之夜》视频游戏制造商 Epic Games 之间的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-epic-games-spat-is-matter-priority-eu-industry-chief-says-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 17:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
